  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《锈翅-逃离我的家乡》是一款<strong>互动音画小说</strong>，在游戏中“你”的选择将影响角色的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的灵感来源于《守望先锋》的一则树洞投稿，描绘了山中因家庭原因而辍学的少女，在接触到网络之后走出故乡的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/da1a84b7f368910fd9ec19cf0fe4594d.avif?t=1744865842\" width=600 height=113 /></span>    - 我想逃离我的家乡。那一天，我突然觉得我不应属于这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      我从小在大山里的小镇中长大，从山的这一头到那一头，这就是我生活的全部。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      高中辍学后，我来到注塑厂打工，日复一日地在流水线不变的工作，看着工厂里那些比我年长的阿姨，我仿佛看到了自己未来的模样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      就算未来能够结婚生子，也是继续在工厂里打工，重复我现在的生活。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      直到有一天，我去了镇上的网吧，接触到了外面的世界，认识了在城市生活的阿澈。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      我下定决心，想要逃离我的家乡。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/cbb32ceaed7aa018c4cd5d0da5ccd861.avif?t=1744865842\" width=600 height=113 /></span>    - 游戏以清新的像素风格，来还原写实的生活，力求增加代入感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/883ce81fe6ba921b3f20b4661a329fb5.poster.avif?t=1744865842\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/883ce81fe6ba921b3f20b4661a329fb5.webm?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/883ce81fe6ba921b3f20b4661a329fb5.mp4?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/4e3d2b80202c9dd584f30b463c720502.poster.avif?t=1744865842\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/4e3d2b80202c9dd584f30b463c720502.webm?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/4e3d2b80202c9dd584f30b463c720502.mp4?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/2192adf960199d9970cddacfed91bb71.poster.avif?t=1744865842\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/2192adf960199d9970cddacfed91bb71.webm?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/2192adf960199d9970cddacfed91bb71.mp4?t=1744865842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985750/extras/a683997e523c459c6ded11a1c85bf592.avif?t=1744865842\" width=600 height=113 /></span>    - - 4小时感人肺腑的沉浸式故事体验，故事的结局因你的选择而不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 全中文语音配音，配角方言口音还原大山生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 60张以上全原创像素CG与场景，总计超过100张差分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 30首原创BGM与1首主题曲，由独立音乐人RAiNSE雨观、中国游戏创新大赛音频奖得主寻雾、音乐艺术家王秋予、赵雪丹妮共同操刀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 部分场景采用动态像素风格，并加入了2段动态过场动画。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入《锈翅》交流群：701378368</strong></p>",
